<br>
It is with great pleasure that I see you will join the League of Honour.   At this point we should be able to better protect you from the shadowed forces, as well as offer a place where you can pursue your scholarly investigations.<br>
<br>
I however need to point out that our problem with the League of Shadows is a rather old problem, and that you should take no blame for this current round of .....confrontations.<br>
<br>
Indeed, I hear rumours that the evil have infested an island deep in Kunark, and wonder if I should soon take a force south to investigate.  A wandering druid brought a tale of a dark, cold city on an island, shrouded in mists.  Perhaps an evil dream, but I feel in my heart it is not so.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub219.ezboard.com/bnecropolis">pub219.ezboard.com/bnecropolis</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Perhaps you will wish to join us on this journey Sergian?  <br>
<br>
Sincerely<br>
Meledi Weaver<br>
League of Honour<br>
Bard of 59 Songs <p><img border=0 src="http://home.golden.net/~effinger/sig.jpg" /></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showMessageRange?topicID=924.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showPrevMessage?topicID=924.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showNextMessage?topicID=924.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=924.topic&index=25><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.threadControl?topicID=924.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=924.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=924.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub94.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="firionaviefrm1">Firion